24:18.500 --> 24:19.775
He ain't done a lick
of work in his life.

24:19.860 --> 24:21.340
He had to go to football practice.

24:21.420 --> 24:23.412
Coach wanted them to get
in a little extra practice

24:23.500 --> 24:24.775
