24:24.860 --> 24:26.533
Yeah, I got his practice all right.

24:26.620 --> 24:28.896
Running out of here before
he gets his chores done.

24:28.980 --> 24:30.573
Troy,
what is wrong with you this morning?

24:30.660 --> 24:31.776
Don't nothing set right with you.

24:31.860 --> 24:34.216
Go on back in there, go to bed,
and get up on the other side.

24:34.300 --> 24:35.575
Why something got
to be wrong with me?

24:35.660 --> 24:36.730
I ain't said nothing wrong with me.

24:36.820 --> 24:38.300
Well, you got something
to say about everything.

24:38.380 --> 24:40.133
First, it's the numbers,
then it's the way the man

24:40.220 --> 24:42.052
run his restaurant,
then you done got on Cory.

24:42.140 --> 24:43.654
What's it gonna be next?

24:43.780 --> 24:45.931
Take a look up there,
see if the weather suit you.

24:46.020 --> 24:47.500
Or is it gonna be how you
gonna put up this fence

24:47.620 --> 24:48.895
with the clothes
hanging in the yard?

24:48.980 --> 24:50.573
You hit the nail on the head then.

24:50.660 --> 24:52.731
I know you like I know
the back of my hand.

24:52.820 --> 24:54.652
Come on in here and get
you some more coffee,

24:54.740 --> 24:56.299
see if that don't straighten you up.

24:56.420 --> 24:58.059
'Cause you ain't right this morning.

