26:49.820 --> 26:52.130
You want to see my key?

26:53.700 --> 26:57.296
That's my own key. Ain't nobody
else got a key like that.

26:57.380 --> 26:59.212
That's my key for my two rooms.

26:59.300 --> 27:01.257
That's good, Gabe.
Got your own key, that's good.

27:01.340 --> 27:02.535
You hungry, Gabe?

27:02.620 --> 27:04.259
I was just fixing to
cook Troy some breakfast.

27:04.380 --> 27:07.020
I'll take some biscuits.
You got some biscuits?

27:08.980 --> 27:12.860
