sit there and eat us them biscuits.

27:21.340 --> 27:23.935
And then Saint Peter
would go off to sleep,

27:24.020 --> 27:25.613
and tell me to wake him up

27:25.700 --> 27:27.976
when it's time to open the
Gates for the Judgment.

27:28.060 --> 27:32.532
Well, come on, I'll make
you a big batch of biscuits.

27:32.660 --> 27:36.574
Hey, Troy. Saint Peter got your
name in his book. I seen it.

27:36.660 --> 27:38.538
It say, "Troy Maxson."

27:38.820 --> 27:40.698
I say, "I know him.

27:40.780 --> 27:44.091
"He got the same
name like what I got.

27:44.180 --> 27:46.137
"That's my brother."

27:47.540 --> 27:49.850
How many times you gonna
tell me that, Gabe?

27:49.940 --> 27:52.978
Ain't got my name in the book.
