but I know it's in there.

28:15.380 --> 28:18.737
He got a great big book!

28:18.820 --> 28:21.494
He got everybody's name
what was ever been born.

28:21.580 --> 28:22.855
That's what he told me.

28:23.580 --> 28:26.778
But I seen your name.
I seen it with my own eye.

28:26.860 --> 28:27.850
Come in the house.

28:27.940 --> 28:29.340
Rose gonna fix you
something to eat now.

28:29.420 --> 28:31.855
I ain't hungry. I done had breakfast

28:32.900 --> 28:34.937
with Aunt Jemima!

28:35.020 --> 28:38.172
She come by, cook me up a
whole mess of flapjacks!

28:38.260 --> 28:39.933
All right. Come on, let's go
in the house. Rose fix us...

28:40.060 --> 28:41.460
Remember how we used
to eat them flapjacks?

28:41.540 --> 28:42.690
Yes, I remember. Come on now.

28:42.780 --> 28:43.896
- I got to go!
- Gabe!

28:44.020 --> 28:45.579
- I got to go!
